cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to improve fine-grained entity typing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves entity linking, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed deep neural model also involves training and optimization, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
